Four killed and one sustained critical injuries when two vehicles collided head on with each other on the N1 approximately 3km before the Kroonvaal Toll Plaza on Sunday.On arrival ER24 paramedics found the one vehicle standing in the middle of the highway. The other vehicle was found several meters off the road in a nearby veld.ER24 Spokesperson Werner Vermaak said &#8220;One person was found with fatal injuries in the vehicle standing in the veld. Sadly, he was declared dead on the scene&#8221;.A critically injured occupant from the same vehicle was rushed to Parys Hospital by another private service. And three men were found with fatal injuries in the vehicle standing on the highway. And they were declared dead on the scene.The cause of the collision is not yet known.-TNA Reporter 